A Kiambu politician has been charged with attempting to rape a campaigner in his car on Thursday last week.On Monday, Tigoni-Ngecha MCA hopeful George Ndung&rsquo;u (pictured), shielding his face with his hand, denied the charges.He also denied indecently assaulting the woman and injuring her.Limuru senior resident magistrate Karen Njalale released him on Sh250,000 bond with a surety of a similar amount.